  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIn some cases when text is appended directly before or after mention, mention formatting is applied to the newly added text.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n1. Add mention (the only input in the input field)\r\n2. Position cursor at the beginning\r\n3. Type in some new letters\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNew text shouldn't have mention's formatting\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nNewly added text becomes part of the mention\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20650004/185635499-b848088d-89cb-429d-853a-46f1ca1965a2.mp4\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version:\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu\r\n\r\n",
